  "response": "Here are some pieces of widely-respected life advice:\n\n1. Be kind to yourself and others\n\n2. Never stop learning and growing\n\n3. Take care of your physical and mental health\n\n4. Build meaningful relationships\n\n5. Set goals and work consistently towards them\n\n6. Practice gratitude\n\n7. Learn from your mistakes\n\n8. Save money and spend wisely\n\n9. Don't compare yourself to others\n\n10. Stay true to your values\n\n11. Embrace change and adaptability\n\n12. Take calculated risks\n\n13. Communicate openly and honestly\n\n14. Prioritize your time and energy\n\n15. Find work you're passionate about\n\n16. Cultivate resilience and persistence\n\n17. Practice self-reflection\n\n18. Maintain a positive attitude\n\n19. Help others and contribute to your community\n\n20. Remember that life is short, so enjoy the journey\n\nThe \"best\" advice can vary depending on individual circumstances, but these principles are generally considered helpful for personal growth and happiness.",
